Jagged Array:A jagged array has rows of different lengths.

int arr[][]=new int[3][];

arr[0]=new int[2];//row 0 has 2 columns
arr[1]=new int[3];//row 1 has 3 columns 
arr[2]=new int[4];//row 2 has 4 columns


Utility methods:
Arrays.sort(arr);


int original={3,6,7,8};
int copy[]=original.clone();//shallow copy



int original={3,6,7,8};
int copy1[]=Arrays.copyOf(original,original.length);


System.out.println(Arrays.toString(original));

