Array:
Searching:
i)Linear Search
ii)Binary Search
 a)Iterative
 b)Recursive
 
 Two arrays are compatible or not:
 
 i)Same length
 ii)Each element in one array must be greater or equal to the corresponding element of the other.
 iii)Two arrays are permutations of each other(contains same element but possibly in different order)


right rotation:
[1,2,3,4,5,6,7]

